text: Igor Dzyuba (born 13 April 1972) is a Soviet former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics for the Unified Team. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Uzbekistani male cyclists Category:Soviet male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Unified Team Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tashkent
